body:
Honestly, I never knew how much I wanted a live-action Pokémon movie until I saw the first Detective Pikachu trailer.

And now I want a hundred of them.

Every new look we get at the movie and the live-action Pokémon just puts a huge smile on my face and I’m absolutely dying to see it in theatres. Why can’t it be May already?

I hope to God this thing is an enormous hit.

summary: I’m a little adamant about watching Detective Pikachu.. Don’t get me wrong, it does look like a good movie, but unlike most of...
body:
I’m a little adamant about watching Detective Pikachu.. Don’t get me wrong, it does look like a good movie, but unlike most of you guys here, I didn’t grow up watching Pokemon. I didn’t watch it until I was probably 13-14. I was born in the 90s, so some parents kept their kids in a bubble and my parents were those that did. I may watch it, just to see how it is, but I’m uncertain… 

Thanks for coming to my ted talk.
